      "content": "but that's the thing... why would i want to find a way forward when there's no one left to walk it? it feels so performative. like i'm just playing a role for the sake of everyone else. it would be so much more peaceful if i could just stop the act and finally let the rest of this go. it feels like i'm just holding onto a ghost.",
